      "concept": "Actual-Capacity Battery Power Bank Case",
      "rationale": "Shoppers are frustrated by 'fake' power bank claims where the case cannot charge a phone or drains instantly; a variant with a transparently labeled, verified-capacity power bank would satisfy heavy-usage users."
    },
    {
      "concept": "Ergonomic Fit Kit Variant",
      "rationale": "Many users report discomfort, size mismatches, or earbuds falling out; a model that includes multiple sizes of silicon tips (specifically marketed as a fit-focused set) would solve the common complaint that 'they don't fit well'."
